reviewText: I personally love bowhunting.  What this joker is doing?  Not so much.

Not a bad hunting show at all.  Especially because it is free to stream on Amazon Prime.  Eddie is a fun guy to watch on these hunts.  I am not even a big archery hunter but the show is still something I like.  To be honest I have watched almost all of his instant watch stuff on Prime.  Worth the watch for sure.  If you like hunting these are fun to watch.
